We start with a diagram, including median $\overline{QN}$, which is also an altitude.  Let the medians intersect at $G$, the centroid of the triangle.


[asy]
size(100);
pair P,Q,R,M,NN;
P = (0,0);
Q = (0.5,0.9);
R = (1,0);
NN = (0.5,0);
M = (Q+R)/2;
